# BTC Morning Brief — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys.
# NEVER commit .env to version control.
#
# Expo automatically exposes variables prefixed with EXPO_PUBLIC_ to the
# JavaScript bundle via process.env. No extra packages required (SDK 49+).
# After editing .env, restart the Expo dev server (npx expo start) to pick
# up the new values.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Tiingo Crypto API — free tier works (10-min OHLCV bars + daily candles)
# Get your key at: https://www.tiingo.com/account/api/token
EXPO_PUBLIC_TIINGO_TOKEN=9221765e328341493c8a665611b1f18835959588

# Nansen API — paid, required for on-chain intelligence layer
# Token Flows · Smart Money Movements · Wallet Profiler
# Get your key at: https://www.nansen.ai/
EXPO_PUBLIC_NANSEN_API_KEY=ynIZQdy22IJUilFeeqcsRvJoW0ojhQGcx

